{"type": "article", "id": 17710, "title": "香槟包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-18T06:40:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607104227o2Npxdy5b9KUnXVL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tButterflyCannon 是一家专为时尚精品店做设计的事务所，他们曾为Chandon 设计过多种包装。这次的假期主题主要用了香槟的颜色，在白色的胶套上面印满了手写粗体文字，大小不一，自由而活泼。其余的说明文字用了黑体，显得正式。香槟色本身带有一种时尚和优雅，在白色的映衬下显得简洁大方。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144851vVBxJ0cuq53oWbfI.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"622\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.15613383\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261448514vEdNkY6X0gU8K5S.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"303\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56319703\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144852vFeZVYmb2lnDE1rA.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"807\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}